These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, epic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
2. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
3. the person watching epic movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | cola   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | disaster   |
| Sport         | basketball | volleyball |
| Transport     | motorbike | snowmobile    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: banana, raspberry
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, musical
2 different pets are kept: hamster, pony
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching superhero movies is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | banana     | raspberry |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | superhero  |
| Pet           | pony         | hamster     |
| Transport     | bike   | helicopter    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite
The people have 2 different jobs:  pilot, teacher
2 different pets are kept: pony, bird
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the teacher##3
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the teacher##1
3. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | sprite     | juice |
| Job         | teacher | pilot    |
| Pet         | pony         | bird        |
| Transport   | jet-ski         | boat    |

