.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate
There 2 different types of food: plum, lemon
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, filmmaking
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, dubstep
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | lemonade |
| Food          | lemon   | plum  |
| Hobby         | singing | filmmaking     |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | dubstep         |

